title: CDDIS_DORIS_products_quaternions
summary: Satellite attitude information from satellites with Doppler Orbitography by Radiopositioning Integrated on Satellite (DORIS) receivers. Files include attitude quaternions for the body of the spacecraft and solar panel angular positions.
